        "subject": "LU-6081 lfs: added room for mdt-index option to lfs migrate",
        "message": "LU-6081 lfs: added room for mdt-index option to lfs migrate\n\nThis option prepares for a future expansion, where the MDT index can\nalso be specified. Currently the MDT index is set to -1, which is the\ndefault index. We do it now to avoid having to change the API later.\n\nSigned-off-by: frank zago <fzago@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I85c2b2d622341c25e62961c8348966e6a63a5545\n"
      },
